title: CANT TRANSFER SERVICE
body: CANT TRANSFER SERVICE    AN ERROR HAS OCCURRED

replies.body: Ahhh!!  Where are you trying to transfer to?  We had a patch over the night, so regions may still be syncing'up.  EUNE is also [undergoing maintenance](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support/U1EoNwo6-sell-me-champion-please), so a transfer won't be available until that's been completed.  Hope that helps!
